  "description": "The Intercranial Meningioma Segmenter is a software tool developed by researchers from Universidad Polit\u00e9cnica de Madrid and Children\u2019s National Hospital for the segmentation and analysis of intercranial meningiomas in magnetic resonance imaging (MRI). Built in Python, it enables precise quantitative analysis of intercranial meningiomas in brain MRI scans to support clinical decision-making in both diagnosis and prognosis.",
